title: primary colorectal adenocarcinoma R001: MSS
extract_protocol_ch1: Surgically isolated colorectal cancers were immediately frozen in liquid nitrogen. Total RNA was extracted from cancer tissue using Trizol reagent (Invitrogen).
label_protocol_ch1: Approximately 5 ug of total RNA was processed to produce biotinylated cRNA targets.
description: colorectal cancer microsatellite status: Microsatellite Stable (MSS)
data_processing: ArrayAssist 3.3 (Stratagene) was used to calculate MAS5.0 calls. The MAS5.0 calls were subsequently quantile normalized and log-2 transformed.
